<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="20.[264,1325,284,1230]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis box="[312,414,884,909]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Remarks</emphasis>
: Four species of 
<taxonomicName box="[635,718,884,909]" class="Polychaeta" family="Terebellidae" genus="Loimia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Terebellida" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[635,718,884,909]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Loimia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are known from the Grand Caribbean region: 
